noria:TroubleTicket_TT20240420_002 noria:troubleTicketPartyIntervention noria:OperationPlan_RestartDBService . # The intervention involved this procedure

# --- Example of a TroubleTicketNote being correlated to a ProcedureExecutionContainer (the TT itself) ---
noria:TroubleTicketNote_TT20240420_001_Note1 noria:troubleTicketNoteCorrelatedExecution noria:TroubleTicket_TT20240420_001 .

